2026-04-30T22:32:33.3921901Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3922642Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3923330Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3924402Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3925283Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3926142Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3926989Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3927821Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3928650Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3929442Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3930099Z 33    -->
2026-04-30T22:32:33.3930756Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
